sections.heading: council; members; bond or insurance
sections.text: All members of the city council of a city of the metropolitan class shall qualify and give bond or evidence of equivalent insurance in the sum of five thousand dollars.SourceLaws 1921, c. 116, art. II, ยง 8, p. 423;C.S.1922, ยง 3533;C.S.1929, ยง 14-208;R.S.1943, ยง 14
